{"tid":265484,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"點解我成日見到IT 同CIVIL 有負面新聞, 但大電就冇乜負面新聞","createTime":"2017-05-31T16:06:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T16:54:52.000Z","uid":108039,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"56a7bae65b86ed723eeb2fb39c651cd7305b85b4","tid":265484,"uid":108039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:06:08.000Z","msg":"我發覺成日都見到IT 同CIVIL 負面新聞, 但唔見大電有<br />\n不如一人一IT ,CIVIL ,EE 負面新聞張貼區 , 睇下邊個MAJOR 較多<br />\n我先<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170327/56487078\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170327%2F56487078&d=sUc5KZ8H5SHklGhWMu8F%2BwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=2571b680\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170327%2F56487078&h=6e5d7a74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170327/56487078</a>"},{"pid":"b67885def2fbfbf3e570404b36b5000cb0ab3183","tid":265484,"uid":108039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:06:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://unwire.pro/2017/05/22/cathay-pacific-layoff-2017/columnist/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.pro%2F2017%2F05%2F22%2Fcathay-pacific-layoff-2017%2Fcolumnist%2F&d=sUc5KZ8H5SHklGhWMu8F%2BwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=02d5deca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.pro/2017/05/22/cathay-pacific-layoff-2017/columnist/</a>"},{"pid":"7d17e0a8f030b0ce28fab87347549a9e4214489e","tid":265484,"uid":108039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:11:10.000Z","msg":"【e-zone 專訊】2017 年過了不足半個月，全球科技公司傳出裁員消息，部分更已「落實」；即使是中國經濟因素、火紅的 VR（虛擬實境）技術也難擋經濟循環的巨輪。繼中興通訊（ZTE）本周初宣布裁員約 3,000 人後，儲存方案商 Seagate Technology（希捷科技）亦宣布將關閉中國蘇州工廠，並裁員 2,000 多人。<br />\n<br />\nSeagate 早在去年 7 月宣布全球重組計劃，縮減生產規模和改善營運效率，並打算在 2017 財年結束前裁走約 14% 員工、即 6,500 人；早在 2015 年 9 月，蘇州工廠已開始分批裁員，今次只是因應計劃提早把它關閉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ctgoodjobs.hk/article/it-%E6%A5%AD%E8%A3%81%E5%93%A1%E5%8F%AA%E6%98%AF%E9%96%8B%E5%A7%8B-%E5%82%B3%E7%B5%B1%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C%EF%BC%8E%E6%96%B0%E8%88%88%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E9%9B%A3%E5%B9%B8%E5%85%8D/1222-17266\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ctgoodjobs.hk%2Farticle%2Fit-%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E8%25A3%2581%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%258F%25AA%25E6%2598%25AF%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%25A7%258B-%25E5%2582%25B3%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E5%2593%2581%25E7%2589%258C%25EF%25BC%258E%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2588%2588%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%258A%2580%25E9%259B%25A3%25E5%25B9%25B8%25E5%2585%258D%2F1222-17266&d=sUc5KZ8H5SHklGhWMu8F%2BwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=529ccac2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ctgoodjobs.hk/article/it-%E6%A5%AD%E8%A3%81%E5%93%A1%E5%8F%AA%E6%98%AF%E9%96%8B%E5%A7%8B-%E5%82%B3%E7%B5%B1%E5%93%81%E7%89%8C%EF%BC%8E%E6%96%B0%E8%88%88%E7%A7%91%E6%8A%80%E9%9B%A3%E5%B9%B8%E5%85%8D/1222-17266</a>"},{"pid":"970bda9fb8894e46afbdf1769c1acf36b0ed577c","tid":265484,"uid":108039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:12:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/n30279civileecs1a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fn30279civileecs1a9.jpg&h=b0e5a819&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4eef7210d4fac838486d7979bffdc98352cdc01","tid":265484,"uid":108039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T16:54:52.000Z","msg":"唔通大電真係咁好行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}